## üéØ Purpose of This Repository
- Stress-test the GSF ideas technically and conceptually  
- Turn abstract vision into implementable system design  
- Invite collaboration on:
  - System architecture  
  - Security models  
  - Governance & legal framing  
  - Prototype-level designs  

